    "description": "《冰球大莽斗》是一款丧心病狂的大杂烩游戏，这里有街机冰球，有打怪过关，还有体育动作，能带你重温昔日与小伙伴们围坐在屏幕前相互耍宝的快乐时光。<br> <br> 玩家需要开启一段史诗冒险，拯救一个古老、繁荣的冰球王国隆德里亚。八位角色个性鲜明，三种职业各尽其责——专职进攻的射手、精通防御的莽卫以及擅长辅助和扰敌的边锋。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/fe33c24795a5e684299ba72cd0b80c9f.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/fe33c24795a5e684299ba72cd0b80c9f.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 你既可以与其他玩家一同组队，在 2v2 模式中挑战单人门将，也可以在经典 3v3 模式中尽情胡搞。游戏重在沟通，但只有技高一筹的队伍才能赢得胜利！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/bf893c025dd019b276570db6d114239c.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/bf893c025dd019b276570db6d114239c.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 精心挑选不同职业，制定团队策略才能破门得分（看运气啦）！玩家可以自由选择射手（进攻）、莽卫（防御）或是边锋（辅助），每一名角色都有专属技能和独到特色，绝对让你深陷其中，欲罢不能！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/07937a46631ff1e0a6ecee8fdae26ddc.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/07937a46631ff1e0a6ecee8fdae26ddc.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 纯粹的冰球运动，但又有稍许不同。结合了更加现代的运动元素，同时加入了角色职业和充当首领怪的门将，让你和亲朋好友重回客厅欢闹时代。享受本地搞事合作的快乐，或与好友甚至是路人玩家一起在线联网！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/1b90f91d4c3911abc18a15c1387b23d1.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/1b90f91d4c3911abc18a15c1387b23d1.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 你不仅要当心其他玩家，还要小心门将会不遗余力地随时拦住你的精妙进攻。远程抽射？大力攻门？贴身推挡？为了守住球网，门将会竭尽全力摧毁你的一切企图。<br> <br> 在《冰球大莽斗》的故事模式中，门将则会化身为真正的 Boss。每一个都会教你如何做一名出色的冰球手，进而逐渐掌握各种冰球技巧，为你之后的 PVP 战斗做足充分准备！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/e131602780c8d50e3576cf12d748f888.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/e131602780c8d50e3576cf12d748f888.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 《冰球大莽斗》提供各式各样的球场环境让你和好友尽情横冲直撞，从白雪皑皑的海岸，到曾经繁荣一时的水产市场，再到神秘莫测的奇幻世界。每一处场景都有独创的玩法机制、情景危机和等待被你击败的门将。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/3ac15851741eb44d5b5f9b5efedddb43.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/3ac15851741eb44d5b5f9b5efedddb43.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 踏上一段拯救冰球宇宙的旅程吧！在单人模式下展开冒险，击败布偶大王和他手下的布偶们，拯救全世界！随着关卡推进，你将解锁更多角色，并一步步揭开冰球宇宙骚乱背后的惊天大秘密！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/ae354a2c90de81f8ece1679a490d4f9b.poster.avif?t=1727358066\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1484180/extras/ae354a2c90de81f8ece1679a490d4f9b.webm?t=1727358066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br> 借助升级系统，你可以自定义快速表情和角色皮肤，让游戏体验更上一层楼。参与比赛、赢取金币、进店购物。别省钱，全力释放你的血拼之力！多多交流，冲击高分！记得友谊第一哦！",
